{"tid":421954,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人醫返好頸椎病","createTime":"2017-10-02T16:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T04:55:00.000Z","uid":1833,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"a5379398d8943fc4791739addf47547c7b82900c","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"平時搬下重野<br />\n要用力<br />\n條頸都會唔舒服<br />\n有時打機坐得耐又會唔舒服<br />\n條頸長期覺得好緊<br />\n當抬高頭拉一拉條頸就會舒服少少<br />\n試過做針灸<br />\n無乜用<br />\n個中醫叫我轉睇骨傷科<br />\n有冇人有類似經驗<br />\n我應該睇咩最好？"},{"pid":"e3a8443bb588aeab99685f0d1d9cc8d624193ec2","tid":421954,"uid":8598,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"留名，我應該同你相同情況"},{"pid":"682530f5415dfd2c3d5ac476d3e96f99536d4cf7","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:13:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名，我應該同你相同情況</blockquote><br />\n真係都市病嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然個中醫話好小事<br />\n但都想快啲搞返掂<br />\n我個觸發點應該係長期做gym用得太多頸力導致勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54e92ad23fcbc568b904a1470864bb3501404a17","tid":421954,"uid":38540,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:14:46.000Z","msg":"姿勢先係治本 坐係度用電腦 爬係度睇書 要保持耳仔對正搏頭 收下爬 <br />\n以前都因為咁長期疲勞 頸緊搏痛 而家留意返好好多"},{"pid":"556b476f405b258cfe02ce1919a99f1b5d7355a4","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姿勢先係治本 坐係度用電腦 爬係度睇書 要保持耳仔對正搏頭 收下爬 <br />\n以前都因為咁長期疲勞 頸緊搏痛 而家留意返好好多</blockquote><br />\n會留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f6697744173f5d2eff3b81885f8ff3c7d44464","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67358898020995c009563efbca68726c22777d81","tid":421954,"uid":47109,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>姿勢先係治本 坐係度用電腦 爬係度睇書 要保持耳仔對正搏頭 收下爬 <br />\n以前都因為咁長期疲勞 頸緊搏痛 而家留意返好好多</blockquote><br />\n收下爬真係好重要"},{"pid":"7f7fd65698aa609a79f90ddb335b0b6618bb1190","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"其實有啲想睇脊醫<br />\n不過好撚貴<br />\n但其實貴唔係問題<br />\n如果搞得掂嘅話<br />\n問題係驚俾完幾千銀又搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f95d858b03c006a3d1953f53218f7d7d911b634b","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T16:34:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fce6f8ba71d3d1c0aadca4115c0bf82ba3e10c85","tid":421954,"uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"做咩叫人睇巫醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2759217671a2e3a7ee2352c7beca9151d6fc3f1c","tid":421954,"uid":126005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T22:50:26.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2f157804716632ecd70ddb271aedcb8db3c72ae6","tid":421954,"uid":92800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T03:13:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平時搬下重野<br />\n要用力<br />\n條頸都會唔舒服<br />\n有時打機坐得耐又會唔舒服<br />\n條頸長期覺得好緊<br />\n當抬高頭拉一拉條頸就會舒服少少<br />\n試過做針灸<br />\n無乜用<br />\n個中醫叫我轉睇骨傷科<br />\n有冇人有類似經驗<br />\n我應該睇咩最好？</blockquote><br />\n你平時做野都要搬搬枱枱，或者長期用電腦？可以留意下姿勢，如果做完治療，姿勢唔好，都會復發或者加重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時自己長時間用完電腦，會唔會做番啲運動放鬆番？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果你搵骨推專長嘅中醫，會針對治療番你頸椎同肌肉，例如牽引運動，扳法，糾正頸椎位置；推拿滾按針灸，疏通氣血。"},{"pid":"c58cec4b560617bca424dc096e6b42c68b1d5d7d","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T05:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平時搬下重野<br />\n要用力<br />\n條頸都會唔舒服<br />\n有時打機坐得耐又會唔舒服<br />\n條頸長期覺得好緊<br />\n當抬高頭拉一拉條頸就會舒服少少<br />\n試過做針灸<br />\n無乜用<br />\n個中醫叫我轉睇骨傷科<br />\n有冇人有類似經驗<br />\n我應該睇咩最好？</blockquote><br />\n你平時做野都要搬搬枱枱，或者長期用電腦？可以留意下姿勢，如果做完治療，姿勢唔好，都會復發或者加重。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時自己長時間用完電腦，會唔會做番啲運動放鬆番？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 如果你搵骨推專長嘅中醫，會針對治療番你頸椎同肌肉，例如牽引運動，扳法，糾正頸椎位置；推拿滾按針灸，疏通氣血。</blockquote><br />\n試過針灸<br />\n無乜用<br />\n嚟緊打算試骨傷科"},{"pid":"b48868f589fe6909dd6edbcdcc1f9b53fb17c8e5","tid":421954,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b5815c136fa1f158229668e8cf96c1a1624093","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T16:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7009059e5b132491671f58974a321d7bf64e2a1","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:29:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dd20d9213e8c329780c0669fea33a25695dd76","tid":421954,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4866d64d6c0e74a6b436be0883adac82b33e6898","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651be004107c382da4a696dfd641af766b6f1c35","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"到底睇咩醫生好"},{"pid":"3767bbeb88f179f9038594a9b326cbd532010f91","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"到底睇咩醫生好"},{"pid":"5edbb676a88caba5cd2b81347df4f2c9dc07670e","tid":421954,"uid":3520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"f8168665688922c29932ba2f845d737baac4b834","tid":421954,"uid":26014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:41:14.000Z","msg":"我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f4a0510ba29b9eb0f6150bbd06f47078a9bc3c","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咩情況？<br />\n錢唔係問題啊<br />\n睇得返好就得<br />\n問題係唔知睇咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脊醫定物理治療定骨科定中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b550d30d17df0c343afbe5d47cdc7aa8b5f6faca","tid":421954,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咩情況？<br />\n錢唔係問題啊<br />\n睇得返好就得<br />\n問題係唔知睇咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脊醫定物理治療定骨科定中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係本身膊頭好緊，企係度又坐係度又好，一路扯住扯住咁<br />\n忍咗半年愈來愈嚴重，終於頂唔順去睇，一開始睇針灸同推拿都睇唔好<br />\n最後睇物治療，不來條頸椎歪咗，自己都摸到<br />\n而加拉咗6次頸，冇咁辛苦，同埋坐係度個人要有咁直坐咁直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586fc266fcf1b6c97ca69b9a05ebf64a9cf2c8c6","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T09:49:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咩情況？<br />\n錢唔係問題啊<br />\n睇得返好就得<br />\n問題係唔知睇咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脊醫定物理治療定骨科定中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係本身膊頭好緊，企係度又坐係度又好，一路扯住扯住咁<br />\n忍咗半年愈來愈嚴重，終於頂唔順去睇，一開始睇針灸同推拿都睇唔好<br />\n最後睇物治療，不來條頸椎歪咗，自己都摸到<br />\n而加拉咗6次頸，冇咁辛苦，同埋坐係度個人要有咁直坐咁直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打喺邊睇？<br />\n醫院有冇得轉介？<br />\n要睇幾耐先會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2ff679c1b00bfd685a7ea80639b4ef4d8d1eca6","tid":421954,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T11:17:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咩情況？<br />\n錢唔係問題啊<br />\n睇得返好就得<br />\n問題係唔知睇咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脊醫定物理治療定骨科定中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係本身膊頭好緊，企係度又坐係度又好，一路扯住扯住咁<br />\n忍咗半年愈來愈嚴重，終於頂唔順去睇，一開始睇針灸同推拿都睇唔好<br />\n最後睇物治療，不來條頸椎歪咗，自己都摸到<br />\n而加拉咗6次頸，冇咁辛苦，同埋坐係度個人要有咁直坐咁直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打喺邊睇？<br />\n醫院有冇得轉介？<br />\n要睇幾耐先會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n借問聲出面睇物理治癒市價幾多<br />\n我係學校睇左幾次<br />\n一星期睇一次<br />\n改善左小小 次次都叫我下星期複診<br />\n唔知睇幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29c86f3c06c396d21868f18327fa973057c79fe4","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T12:29:49.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打成功睇返好之後有介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfdb4dc50026d14876482c47a0bcabc84da05bd","tid":421954,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咩情況？<br />\n錢唔係問題啊<br />\n睇得返好就得<br />\n問題係唔知睇咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脊醫定物理治療定骨科定中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係本身膊頭好緊，企係度又坐係度又好，一路扯住扯住咁<br />\n忍咗半年愈來愈嚴重，終於頂唔順去睇，一開始睇針灸同推拿都睇唔好<br />\n最後睇物治療，不來條頸椎歪咗，自己都摸到<br />\n而加拉咗6次頸，冇咁辛苦，同埋坐係度個人要有咁直坐咁直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打喺邊睇？<br />\n醫院有冇得轉介？<br />\n要睇幾耐先會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n借問聲出面睇物理治癒市價幾多<br />\n我係學校睇左幾次<br />\n一星期睇一次<br />\n改善左小小 次次都叫我下星期複診<br />\n唔知睇幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇一次要$350，我都冇問醫生睇幾耐，我諗睇幾千銀走唔甩<br />\n我就咁打電話去診所約時間，係公司附近搵，貪夠近放工去"},{"pid":"d843d562406be5798e46a7c764efe883d99c70db","tid":421954,"uid":120854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:10:13.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"35e685a6cad30b30ce59dd00515d2143785afd6b","tid":421954,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:16:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咩情況？<br />\n錢唔係問題啊<br />\n睇得返好就得<br />\n問題係唔知睇咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脊醫定物理治療定骨科定中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係本身膊頭好緊，企係度又坐係度又好，一路扯住扯住咁<br />\n忍咗半年愈來愈嚴重，終於頂唔順去睇，一開始睇針灸同推拿都睇唔好<br />\n最後睇物治療，不來條頸椎歪咗，自己都摸到<br />\n而加拉咗6次頸，冇咁辛苦，同埋坐係度個人要有咁直坐咁直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打喺邊睇？<br />\n醫院有冇得轉介？<br />\n要睇幾耐先會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n借問聲出面睇物理治癒市價幾多<br />\n我係學校睇左幾次<br />\n一星期睇一次<br />\n改善左小小 次次都叫我下星期複診<br />\n唔知睇幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打邊間學校有得睇?"},{"pid":"b01e4aa53d0d85be5f3fa56674ecdf6c8bcc3e70","tid":421954,"uid":92278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:24:54.000Z","msg":"有冇試過啪骨 好正的<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3fd5aa23db2833f5722f7963c7e803f1a9ec56","tid":421954,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我睇緊物理治療，不過真係要預幾千銀睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打咩情況？<br />\n錢唔係問題啊<br />\n睇得返好就得<br />\n問題係唔知睇咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n脊醫定物理治療定骨科定中醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係本身膊頭好緊，企係度又坐係度又好，一路扯住扯住咁<br />\n忍咗半年愈來愈嚴重，終於頂唔順去睇，一開始睇針灸同推拿都睇唔好<br />\n最後睇物治療，不來條頸椎歪咗，自己都摸到<br />\n而加拉咗6次頸，冇咁辛苦，同埋坐係度個人要有咁直坐咁直<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打喺邊睇？<br />\n醫院有冇得轉介？<br />\n要睇幾耐先會好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n借問聲出面睇物理治癒市價幾多<br />\n我係學校睇左幾次<br />\n一星期睇一次<br />\n改善左小小 次次都叫我下星期複診<br />\n唔知睇幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打邊間學校有得睇?</blockquote><br />\nPoly"},{"pid":"ee14490ba57ae1b5674967c9d41de951c8df5e06","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:39:43.000Z","msg":"上網睇過好多分享<br />\n好多都話脊醫又貴又冇用<br />\n我自己都試過中醫針灸<br />\n都完全無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n綜合嚟講最多人推介係物理治療<br />\n仲見到有人話睇咗3,4次就搞掂<br />\n但係去邊間睇好<br />\n公立排我怕我要排返3,5,7年<br />\n定係求其去間私院睇就得？<br />\n定係睇市面上啲物理治療中心<br />\n多到唔知揀邊間<br />\n又差唔多價錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人有推介"},{"pid":"1682230b0701f92d67380767fbb0c7cbb4a56b68","tid":421954,"uid":105561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"同樓主情況好類似 一起身就痛 出名中醫針炙試過無用 <br />\n跟著睇骨科再轉介物理治療<br />\n之後好翻好多 穩定好多 <br />\n跟足指示係屋企拉筋拉<br />\n注意翻係無得根治 不過起碼無keep住痛<br />\n利申 公司醫療包<br />\n一次物理治療通常$500 有d診所有package 一次過買10次$4500咁"},{"pid":"5bbb6a84bf6f78cf882e22cde345b2ff70ae9219","tid":421954,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:27:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>留名，我應該同你相同情況</blockquote><br />\n真係都市病嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然個中醫話好小事<br />\n但都想快啲搞返掂<br />\n我個觸發點應該係長期做gym用得太多頸力導致勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身條頸長唔長 你做gym係咩動作整親 我估係背?"},{"pid":"e7a2e0c09575797af24d30fd0b0c66ac975c1ed2","tid":421954,"uid":90859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T18:33:16.000Z","msg":"我因為長期對電腦加姿勢唔好，頸肩都好傷<br />\n物理治療中醫推拿都試過，無乜用<br />\n<br />\n去睇左間按療，佢係體適能教練，學過筋傷治療，推拿等等<br />\n佢除左用手法去按，仲會係唔同階段會教你拉筋動作同訓練去強化d肌肉<br />\n我睇左兩至三個月，已經好左好多"},{"pid":"02c7c3d31daa24eb2bf6411bec9dcd16b0ffb6e1","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名，我應該同你相同情況</blockquote><br />\n真係都市病嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然個中醫話好小事<br />\n但都想快啲搞返掂<br />\n我個觸發點應該係長期做gym用得太多頸力導致勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身條頸長唔長 你做gym係咩動作整親 我估係背?</blockquote><br />\n長啊<br />\n觸發點係推胸<br />\n但我估都係長期用得太多頸力導致勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"166f8c1b1d30e02dba117d8d2bc6a446a5b3bab9","tid":421954,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T02:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名，我應該同你相同情況</blockquote><br />\n係咪入秋後會嚴重左?"},{"pid":"f0ddfa3bbda8a3dde092186dd89934a4e24ce1dc","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dd2dc629bf510ba4753449da44b2a2fcfc78e5b","tid":421954,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面咪有人叫你睇PT囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"249aa7fd782d10942f456d7ee1b933fa67b010cf","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面咪有人叫你睇PT囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想睇下有冇人有介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8eae1075c0dc66991f5404dccb5cb770298fb10","tid":421954,"uid":39245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:28:52.000Z","msg":"初中有脊柱側彎症, 好似向右7度定8度<br />\n最後留意到應該係成日趴係度睇書/電視/訓覺<br />\n<br />\n之後改左個壞習慣, 好似一兩年之後落到去4-5度"},{"pid":"dc4f2f2d3ac6578e030b3db7f096e40d92b658d7","tid":421954,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:18:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>留名，我應該同你相同情況</blockquote><br />\n真係都市病嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然個中醫話好小事<br />\n但都想快啲搞返掂<br />\n我個觸發點應該係長期做gym用得太多頸力導致勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身條頸長唔長 你做gym係咩動作整親 我估係背?</blockquote><br />\n長啊<br />\n觸發點係推胸<br />\n但我估都係長期用得太多頸力導致勞損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係長頸人士 都幾煩 <br />\n<br />\n打拳或者美式足球既人都會練頸 我覺得要練下頸 (構想階段中)"},{"pid":"18731232288dffbfaad5bf1f42a3663db293e2c9","tid":421954,"uid":143540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:33:32.000Z","msg":"無得醫的，只有抒援。試過哂 針灸 拔罐 推拿 物理治療 骨科專科 胸肺科專科"},{"pid":"48b294c53a926fb662feba7e30ce3f8f5da9558f","tid":421954,"uid":143540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無得醫的，只有抒援。試過哂 針灸 拔罐 推拿 物理治療 骨科專科 胸肺科專科</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同埋脊醫"},{"pid":"84df9cbc62d894bae982488be50cf8a3d12af8ae","tid":421954,"uid":52275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我因為長期對電腦加姿勢唔好，頸肩都好傷<br />\n物理治療中醫推拿都試過，無乜用<br />\n<br />\n去睇左間按療，佢係體適能教練，學過筋傷治療，推拿等等<br />\n佢除左用手法去按，仲會係唔同階段會教你拉筋動作同訓練去強化d肌肉<br />\n我睇左兩至三個月，已經好左好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想睇你講間clinic <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔方便開名就tg講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d047ffb8964336de8645006bdb63188fc2551114","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T11:56:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無得醫的，只有抒援。試過哂 針灸 拔罐 推拿 物理治療 骨科專科 胸肺科專科</blockquote><br />\n咁撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64cf8506114b2219d4f53d28528c4fffdb9d2214","tid":421954,"uid":1833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T12:17:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaefdc7f09450f5c5e50dd4f4c95525f0e98cdd5","tid":421954,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T15:32:06.000Z","msg":"拿拿臨搵個專業嘅睇咗咩事先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" cl